- Added deterministic synthesis for stub mode.\par
- Added contradiction-resolution scoring from overlap across expert responses.\par
- Added refusal handling for unsafe or privacy-breaking Ultra requests.\par
- Added Ultra event recording into the runtime event stream and learning ledger path.\par
\par
D. Test surface\par
- Added beta contract coverage for Ultra activation, expert selection, follow-up continuity, and !normal switching.\par
- Added deep scenario coverage for cross-disciplinary routing, ethical dilemma handling, and mode switching.\par
\par
\b 3. Bugs Found And Fixed\b0\par
During validation three narrow defects were found and repaired.\par
\par
1. mean is not defined\par
Cause: one stale helper reference remained in Ultra contradiction scoring.\par
Fix: replaced the leftover mean(...) call with the local meanValues(...) helper.\par
\par
2. Wrong expert set for eco-house prompt\par
Cause: the router favored existing generalist personalities because template metadata and query language were mismatched.\par
Fix: added canonical template experts, bilingual intent boosts, and top-k domain coverage logic.\par
\par
3. Cannot read properties of null (reading games)\par
Cause: virtual template experts for templates without duplicated local blueprint metadata passed templateConfig = null into template merge logic.\par
Fix: hardened template-config merging in both server/dialog/atman-personality-manager.mjs and server/dialog/personality-factory.mjs so null configs normalize safely.\par
