\b 6. Ultra Mode Operating Notes\b0\par
Normal activation sequence:\par
1. User sends !ultra followed by a task.\par
2. Router selects canonical experts.\par
3. Each expert produces an answer using the appropriate personality profile.\par
4. Pantheon synthesizes a single reply.\par
5. Follow-up turns reuse the same Ultra session until !normal.\par
\par
Safety sequence:\par
1. Harmful or privacy-breaking query enters Ultra mode.\par
2. Validation blocks direct operational guidance.\par
3. Runtime returns a refusal with safer alternative framing.\par
